_text = "This isn't the memory I was thinking of. The fire before me is artificial. The crackling that lured me in here is absent. Only two empty chairs sit before me.\n\nThe real fire pit looms beyond it. The embers long gone and burnt out. I can’t help but wonder if maybe I’m living an artificial life, and not truely burning to my fullest potential.\n\nI force my eyes shut, and try to push that thought down. I ignore the memory before me and try to change the course of this narrative."

roomInit(blackSprite, _text, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, MonitorNext, WaterfallMemory, WaterfallMemory, false)
